'''Mistryl battle language''' was a special language that was spoken by the [[Mistryl Shadow Guard]] when they were engaged in battle. Its main purpose, as well as its major advantage, was that it provided a means of swift, on-the-field communication that maintained the greater degree of security which came with such cryptic speech.

